Github pages documentation for the ansible project
==================================================

How do I.....

Pull in the git submodule?
``````````````````````````

  From a fresh checkout:

    $ git submodule init


Update the git submodule hash?
``````````````````````````````

    $ cd ansible
    $ git pull
    $ cd ..
    $ git add ansible


Build this crazy thing?
```````````````````````

  First, you need these installed:
    * asciidoc
    * python sphinx

  Then you can:

    $ make

  or,

    $ make viewdocs

  to open the built docs in your web browser.
